詹妮弗·安妮斯顿表示，她已经“彻底”取消文化了：“没有救赎吗？” https://www.nme.com/news/film/jennifer-aniston-says-so-over-cancel-culture-no-redemption-3487212?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jennifer-aniston-says-so-over-取消文化无救赎Adam StarkeyWed, 23 Aug 2023 08:51:41 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3487212 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·安妮斯顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不会把所有人都归入哈维·韦恩斯坦的篮子里”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jennifer-aniston-says-so-over-cancel-culture-no-redemption-3487212">詹妮弗·安妮斯顿 (Jennifer Aniston) 发帖表示，她已经“彻底”取消文化了：“没有救赎了吗？”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·安妮斯顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Jennifer-Aniston-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jennifer-aniston">詹妮弗·安妮斯顿</a>批评了“取消文化”的想法，称她并没有“把每个人都放在哈维·韦恩斯坦的篮子里”。</p><p> 《<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>老友记》</em></a>的演员在接受<a href="https://www.wsj.com/style/jennifer-aniston-morning-show-season-3-59413d2f" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《华尔街日报》</em></a>采访时回忆了她与这位名誉扫地的制片人的遭遇，这引发了取消文化的话题。</p><p> “我已经厌倦了取消文化，”安妮斯顿说。 “我可能只是因为这么说而被取消了。我只是不明白这意味着什么……没有救赎吗？我不知道。我不会把所有人都归入哈维·韦恩斯坦的范畴。”</p><p>谈到自己与韦恩斯坦的不愉快遭遇时，安妮斯顿补充道：“他不是一个男人，你会说，‘天哪，我迫不及待地想和哈维一起出去玩。’”绝不。你实际上会说，‘哦，上帝，好吧，忍住吧。’ </p><figure id="attachment_3346991" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3346991" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3346991" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Jennifer-Aniston-HWP_Lifetime-awards.jpg" alt="詹妮弗·安妮斯顿" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Jennifer-Aniston-HWP_Lifetime-awards.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Jennifer-Aniston-HWP_Lifetime-awards-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Jennifer-Aniston-HWP_Lifetime-awards-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Jennifer-Aniston-HWP_Lifetime-awards-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Jennifer-Aniston-HWP_Lifetime-awards-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Jennifer-Aniston-HWP_Lifetime-awards-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3346991" class="wp-caption-text">詹妮弗·安妮斯顿透露她“讨厌”社交媒体。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>“实际上我记得，他来看我看电影，向我推销一部电影。我确实记得有意识地让一个人留在我的拖车里。”作为回应，韦恩斯坦告诉该刊物，安妮斯顿“从未与我发生过任何不舒服的事情”。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jennifer-aniston-turns-off-instagram-comments-jamie-foxx-anti-semitism-backlash-3479946">安妮斯顿因公开谴责杰米·福克斯的 Instagram 帖子而受到网上批评</a>，一些人认为该帖子具有反犹太主义色彩。</p><p>今年早些时候，这位演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jennifer-aniston-says-theres-a-whole-generation-of-people-who-find-friends-offensive-3422541">讨论了多年来对<em>《老友记》</em>的反应如何变化</a>，称“整整一代人”现在都认为这部剧“令人反感”。</p><p> “有些事情从来不是故意的，还有一些……好吧，我们应该仔细考虑一下，但我认为没有像现在这样的敏感性，”安妮斯顿说。</p><p> “喜剧在发展，电影也在发展。现在有点棘手，因为你必须非常小心，这对喜剧演员来说真的很难，因为喜剧的美妙之处在于我们取笑自己，取笑生活。”</p><p>她补充道：“你可以拿一个偏执狂开玩笑，然后开怀大笑。那太歇斯底里了。这是为了教育人们了解人们是多么荒谬，但现在我们不允许这样做。”</p><p>近年来，其他一些名人也批评了取消文化，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-cancel-culture-is-appropriation-3376843">利佐</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cate-blanchett-cancel-culture-warns-destined-to-repeat-titanic-tar-actor-hollywood-3398474">凯特·布兰切特</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jennifer-aniston-says-so-over-cancel-culture-no-redemption-3487212">詹妮弗·安妮斯顿 (Jennifer Aniston) 发帖表示，她已经“彻底”取消文化了：“没有救赎了吗？”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
